01:10:09,665 --> 01:10:11,125
What is it?
Is it the baby?

1050
01:10:12,459 --> 01:10:14,211
HELEN:
Could I have some water?

1051
01:10:14,378 --> 01:10:16,463
We're almost to the house.
Now, come on.

1052
01:10:16,630 --> 01:10:19,299
