1101
01:15:30,027 --> 01:15:33,113
I put a couple C-notes on him myself.
Did you?

1102
01:15:33,280 --> 01:15:36,616
Hey, you know, I sent a buyer up
to Kilronan the other day

1103
01:15:36,783 --> 01:15:39,953
