1132
01:16:51,108 --> 01:16:52,150
Shit.

1133
01:16:52,317 --> 01:16:54,152
MARTHA:
There you go. You're doing good.

1134
01:16:54,319 --> 01:16:58,615
Come on, honey, push a little harder.
Push. Push, Helen, push!

1135
01:16:58,782 --> 01:17:02,202
